#: _revamp.py:46
msgid ""
"The mail server has the possibility to provide filtering of SPAM mails. It "
"is recommended to activate this option"
msgstr ""

#: _revamp.py:50
msgid ""
"To avoid the delivery of virus infected mails the mail server can check "
"incoming and outgoing mails for known virus signatures. This increases the "
"security and it is highly recommanded to activate this option"
msgstr ""

#: _revamp.py:54
msgid ""
"IMAP is the most common protocol to access a mail server. It is recommended "
"to activate this option"
msgstr ""

#: _revamp.py:59
msgid ""
"To restrict the amount of mails that a user can store on the mail server it "
"si required to activate this option. Via Univention Admin it is possible to "
"define the amount of mails that can be stored by a user (policy mail quota)"
msgstr ""

#: _revamp.py:63
msgid ""
"POP3 is another protocol that can be used to access a mail server. Whne "
"using Outlook as client for UGS, this option must be activate"
msgstr ""

#: _revamp.py:69
msgid ""
"The following option provides the possibility to set a maximum size of "
"incoming and outgoing mails. To large mails may cause a high load on the "
"mail server and thereby may increase respone times. The default value should "
"work well in most scenarios"
msgstr ""

#: _revamp.py:74
msgid ""
"Any information regarding problems or warning an a system are send to an "
"local email account. These mail can be redirected to another global account "
"by setting this option to a valid e-mail address"
msgstr ""
